00:16:44,760 --> 00:16:45,760
[ហុង Jiaoyang, Shi Xiaochun,] Shi Xiaochun ។

356
00:16:45,760 --> 00:16:46,350
[នាយកដ្ឋានរបាំបាឡេ, ទទួលយក] Shi Xiaochun ។

